---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <header class="site-header">
    <span class="header-name">Josh Paris</span>
    <nav class="header-nav">
      <a href="#work">Work</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <h1>Josh Paris</h1>
        <p class="role">PM and Ops lead at early-stage startups.</p>
        <p class="bio">I've spent the last five years inside the operations layer of fintech startups - owning internal tooling, customer support systems, and AI automation work at Lithic and HMBradley. I'm the person who inherits a broken process, figures out what's actually wrong, and builds something that holds.</p>
        <a href="mailto:joshsparis@gmail.com" class="email-cta">joshsparis@gmail.com</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="experience-strip">
      <div class="strip-inner">
        <div class="strip-entry">
          <span class="strip-company">Lithic</span>
          <span class="strip-sep">·</span>
          <span class="strip-role">PM, Internal Tools</span>
          <span class="strip-sep">·</span>
          <span class="strip-dates">2024 - 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="strip-entry">
          <span class="strip-company">HMBradley</span>
          <span class="strip-sep">·</span>
          <span class="strip-role">PM, Support & Ops</span>
          <span class="strip-sep">·</span>
          <span class="strip-dates">2021 - 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="strip-entry">
          <span class="strip-company">Undertime</span>
          <span class="strip-sep">·</span>
          <span class="strip-role">AI Consultant</span>
          <span class="strip-sep">·</span>
          <span class="strip-dates">2025 - Present</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="work" id="work">
      <div class="work-inner">
        <p class="section-label">Selected Work</p>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-company">Undertime</span>
            <span class="card-sep">·</span>
            <span class="card-context">AI Consultant</span>
            <span class="card-sep">·</span>
            <span class="card-dates">2025 - Present</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">AI Email Agent for Insurance Agencies</h2>

          <div class="card-sections">
            <div class="card-section">
              <h3 class="section-header">The Problem</h3>
              <p class="section-body">Insurance agencies were manually qualifying and following up with incoming leads - slow, inconsistent, and entirely dependent on staff availability. Response times varied. Leads fell through.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-section">
              <h3 class="section-header">My Role</h3>
              <p class="section-body">Owned PM and QA for a live AI email agent handling lead qualification and drip sequencing. Wrote the prompt instructions, persona definitions, and output formatting constraints that determine how the agent behaves. Designed a GitHub-integrated QA pipeline that automatically evaluates agent outputs and generates structured feedback reports - creating a repeatable improvement loop without manual review overhead.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-section">
              <h3 class="section-header">How It Works</h3>
              <p class="section-body">The agent receives incoming leads, qualifies them through a structured conversation sequence, and routes warm prospects to a human closer. The QA pipeline runs automatically against every batch of outputs, flags deviations, and produces a feedback summary. Engineering handles the infrastructure - my job is making sure the agent actually does what the client needs it to do.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-tags">
            <span class="tag">AI Implementation</span>
            <span class="tag">Ops Automation</span>
            <span class="tag">QA Systems</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-company">Personal Project</span>
            <span class="card-sep">·</span>
            <span class="card-dates">2025 - Present</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Job Search Agent</h2>

          <div class="card-sections">
            <div class="card-section">
              <h3 class="section-header">The Problem</h3>
              <p class="section-body">Job openings land across dozens of boards. By the time most people see a posting it already has 100+ applications. Even when you're early, you still have to manually read through the description, map it to your experience, and decide if it's worth your time - before spending an hour on an application that gets auto-rejected in 20 minutes.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-section">
              <h3 class="section-header">The System</h3>
              <p class="section-body">A Python automation agent that runs every morning. It scrapes 14 job boards simultaneously, deduplicates the results, scores every posting against my background and interests using AI, and delivers a ranked digest by the time I sit down to work.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-section">
              <h3 class="section-header">How It Works</h3>
              <p class="section-body">Every 24 hours, the agent hits 14 sources - LinkedIn, Wellfound, Himalayas, Remote OK, and direct integrations with Greenhouse, Lever, and Ashby company pages - deduplicates across sources, scores each posting, sorts results into tiers, and pushes a notification with top matches. Directed and shipped with AI as the build layer. Runs autonomously on GitHub Actions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-tags">
            <span class="tag">Internal Tooling</span>
            <span class="tag">Ops Automation</span>
            <span class="tag">AI Implementation</span>
          </div>

          <div class="card-footer">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/Joshwagandha/Josh-os/tree/main/job-search-agent"
              class="card-link"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >View on GitHub &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact" id="contact">
      <div class="contact-inner">
        <h2 class="contact-heading">Get in touch</h2>
        <p class="contact-body">Open to full-time and contract roles in PM, Ops, and implementation at early-stage startups. Remote only.</p>
        <a href="mailto:joshsparis@gmail.com" class="contact-email">joshsparis@gmail.com</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <span>Josh Paris</span>
    <a href="mailto:joshsparis@gmail.com">joshsparis@gmail.com</a>
    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/josh-paris" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── Variables ── */
  :root {
    --bg: #F9F7F4;
    --text-primary: #1A1A1A;
    --text-secondary: #6B6B6B;
    --border: #E5E1DB;
    --accent: #2E5DE0;
    --font-body: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    --font-mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }

  /* ── Global ── */
  :global(body) {
    background-color: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .site-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .header-name {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .header-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .header-nav a {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .header-nav a:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .role {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .bio {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  .email-cta {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .email-cta:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ── Experience strip ── */
  .experience-strip {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
  }

  .strip-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem 3rem;
  }

  .strip-entry {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .strip-company {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .strip-role {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .strip-dates {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .strip-sep {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--border);
  }

  /* ── Work section ── */
  .work {
    padding: 5rem 2rem 6rem;
  }

  .work-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  /* ── Work card ── */
  .work-card {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .card-company {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .card-context,
  .card-dates {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .card-sep {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--border);
  }

  h2.card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .card-sections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Tags ── */
  .card-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .tag {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* ── Card footer ── */
  .card-footer {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .card-link {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .card-link:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ── Contact section ── */
  .contact {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .contact-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2.contact-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .contact-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .contact-email {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .contact-email:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  .site-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .site-footer span {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .site-footer a {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .site-footer a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ── Mobile ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .site-header,
    .hero-inner,
    .strip-inner,
    .work-inner,
    .contact-inner,
    .site-footer {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem 3rem;
    }

    .experience-strip {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .strip-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .work {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem 4rem;
    }

    .work-card {
      padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .contact {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .site-footer {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
